{"tid":2277724,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣未獲邀參與世衛大會　台北對大陸阻撓表示遺憾不滿","createTime":"2020-11-08T16:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T18:53:56.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6dd921d7394e23d9b5e8149e8c67626783852027","tid":2277724,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T16:20:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558973-20201109.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558973-20201109.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq71QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=0013e044\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558973-20201109.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7a61d36b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558973-20201109.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n世界衛生大會今日以視像形式復會，台灣至今未獲邀參與，台北當局對大陸阻撓，以及世衛持續漠視台灣人民的健康人權，表示高度遺憾及強烈不滿。<br />\n<br />\n台灣的外交部說，在台灣爭取參與大會的過程中，國際的聲援越來越強，其中美國再次敦促世衛總幹事譚德塞邀請台灣出席大會，歐洲、非洲、拉丁美洲等地區國家，亦公開表達對台灣的支持，但世衛仍基於政治考量，拒絕邀請台方參會。<br />\n<br />\n當局說，在復會期間，將會規劃舉辦以癌症為主題的網上會議，邀請美歐等國家的官員及專家交流，台方亦會繼續爭取參與世衛會議、機制及活動。"},{"pid":"4e140d8374418dd0f426b68b42d35819c0306806","tid":2277724,"uid":63669,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T16:22:10.000Z","msg":"其實唔需要太care，台灣做下世外桃園食住花生睇who班傻仔搞死自己咪得"},{"pid":"1c978a30ec27a48ee4bc62e7a3b77496f10329d8","tid":2277724,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T16:23:17.000Z","msg":"預左架喇，做樣。"},{"pid":"fd82225c2e9be756d71305890914dede4335026f","tid":2277724,"uid":155095,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T16:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.businessfocus.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/trump525.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.businessfocus.io%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2Ftrump525.jpg&h=3af7de3c&